com.ning.tr13.util
Class VInt

java.lang.Object
  com.ning.tr13.util.VInt

public class VInt
extends Object

Helper class for dealing with Variable-length integers (VInts). Encoding uses big-endian (most-significant byte first) ordering; number of bits in the first byte can vary to allow using couple of leading bits for type marking.
